\section build_release_swig_windows_sec_07 7 reposit

Build the solution, configuration Release (static runtime):

\verbatim
C:\build_ql_1_7_0\reposit\reposit_vc9.sln
\endverbatim

Run the executable:

\verbatim
C:\build_ql_1_7_0\reposit\Examples\C++\bin\ExampleCpp-vc90-mt-s.exe
\endverbatim

Start Excel and load the addin and workbook:

\verbatim
C:\build_ql_1_7_0\reposit\Examples\xl\xll\ExampleXLLStatic-vc90-mt-s.xll
C:\build_ql_1_7_0\reposit\Examples\xl\exampleStatic.xls
\endverbatim

\section build_release_swig_windows_sec_08 8 SimpleLib

Build the solution, configuration Release:

\verbatim
C:\build_ql_1_7_0\swig\Examples\reposit\simple\simple.sln
\endverbatim

Run the executable:

\verbatim
C:\build_ql_1_7_0\swig\Examples\reposit\simple\Release\MainSimpleLibAddin.exe
\endverbatim

Start Excel and load the addin and workbook:

\verbatim
C:\build_ql_1_7_0\swig\Examples\reposit\simple\Release\AddinXl.xll
C:\build_ql_1_7_0\swig\Examples\reposit\simple\AddinXl\AddinXl.xlsx
\endverbatim

\section build_release_swig_windows_sec_09 9 ComplexLib

Build the solution, configuration Release:

\verbatim
C:\build_ql_1_7_0\swig\Examples\reposit\complex\complex.sln
\endverbatim

Run the executable:

\verbatim
C:\build_ql_1_7_0\swig\Examples\reposit\complex\Release\MainComplexLibAddin.exe
\endverbatim

Start Excel and load the addin and workbook:

\verbatim
C:\build_ql_1_7_0\swig\Examples\reposit\complex\Release\AddinXl.xll
C:\build_ql_1_7_0\swig\Examples\reposit\complex\ComplexLibXL\Workbooks\AddinXl.xlsx
\endverbatim

\section build_release_swig_windows_sec_10 10 QuantLibAddin

Build the solution, configuration Release (static runtime):

\verbatim
C:\build_ql_1_7_0\QuantLibAddin2\QuantLibAddin_vc9.sln
\endverbatim

Run the executable:

\verbatim
C:\build_ql_1_7_0\QuantLibAddin2\Release\MainQuantLibAddin.exe
\endverbatim

\section build_release_swig_windows_sec_11 11 Build QuantLibXL

<b>Basic</b> build - open VC solution
<tt>QuantLibXL2\\QuantLibXL_basic_vc9.sln</tt>.

<b>Full</b> build - open VC solution
<tt>QuantLibXL2\\QuantLibXL_full_vc9.sln</tt>.

Choose configuration <tt>Release (static runtime)</tt> and do <tt>Build | Build Solution</tt>.

The build process creates the %QuantLibXL binary file
<tt>QuantLibXL2\\xll\\QuantLibXL-vc90-mt-s-1_7_0.xll</tt>.  Instructions for
loading the addin are provided in the QuantLibXL installation document:
\ref qlxl_install \n

